text: The Fire Inside is the debut studio album by British singer-songwriter Luke Sital-Singh. It was released on 18 August 2014 and peaked at number 43 in the UK Official Chartshttp://www.officialcharts.com/artist/45208/LUKE-SITAL-SINGH/ ==Track listing== ==References== Category:2014 debut albums
title: The Fire Inside (Luke Sital-Singh album)
